  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461840/extras/364ad3e1c448b58b84b71d76d2952987.avif?t=1728674693\" width=570 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Defenders of the Omniverse</strong> is a reverse bullet hell/survivors game with the vibes of the 80’s Saturday morning cartoons, where you take control of heroes from all across the realms of the Omniverse and battle the vile hordes of the Dark Wizard Umbros!  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Battle hordes of enemies, like radioactive wasteland cyborg orcs or metal-skinned space Vikings and many more!</strong> <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461840/extras/9b1db5d9d71cbb6f3ec58909fb7bb6bf.poster.avif?t=1728674693\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461840/extras/9b1db5d9d71cbb6f3ec58909fb7bb6bf.webm?t=1728674693\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461840/extras/9b1db5d9d71cbb6f3ec58909fb7bb6bf.mp4?t=1728674693\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Play as mighty heroes, each with their own passive bonuses and unique Ultimate Ability!</strong> <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461840/extras/5fa86504097eef3121ce18759d0b3c14.poster.avif?t=1728674693\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461840/extras/5fa86504097eef3121ce18759d0b3c14.webm?t=1728674693\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461840/extras/5fa86504097eef3121ce18759d0b3c14.mp4?t=1728674693\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Confront the Ultimate Final Boss, the Dark Wizard Umbros himself, who has random abilities and attacks each time you meet him!</strong> <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461840/extras/d4e1dc2cb70e9038d7231c9364df6641.poster.avif?t=1728674693\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461840/extras/d4e1dc2cb70e9038d7231c9364df6641.webm?t=1728674693\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461840/extras/d4e1dc2cb70e9038d7231c9364df6641.mp4?t=1728674693\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Test your mettle in epic battles with giant bosses.</strong> <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461840/extras/c6fb53a1c7a7ec34951a366bac44e2da.poster.avif?t=1728674693\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461840/extras/c6fb53a1c7a7ec34951a366bac44e2da.webm?t=1728674693\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461840/extras/c6fb53a1c7a7ec34951a366bac44e2da.mp4?t=1728674693\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hand-crafted vibrant art style, inspired by the colorful comic books and cartoons from the 80’s!</strong> <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461840/extras/adf12a0cb500aafa07729a39d821a499.poster.avif?t=1728674693\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461840/extras/adf12a0cb500aafa07729a39d821a499.webm?t=1728674693\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461840/extras/adf12a0cb500aafa07729a39d821a499.mp4?t=1728674693\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collect various powerful weapons and items to create your own devastating builds to crush the foul legions of Evil!</strong> </p></li></ul>",
