oster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461840/extras/adf12a0cb500aafa07729a39d821a499.poster.avif?t=1728674693\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461840/extras/adf12a0cb500aafa07729a39d821a499.webm?t=1728674693\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461840/extras/adf12a0cb500aafa07729a39d821a499.mp4?t=1728674693\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collect various powerful weapons and items to create your own devastating builds to crush the foul legions of Evil!</strong> </p></li></ul>",
